2970 = x * y
x
y
2970 = (x + 165) * (y - 3)
x
y
x
y
x = \frac{2970}{y}
2970 = (\frac{2970}{y} + 165)*(y-3)
\frac{2970}{y-3} = \frac{2970}{y} + 165
\frac{2970}{y} + 165 = \frac{2970}{y} + \frac{165*y}{y} = \frac{2970 + 165*y}{y}
\frac{2970}{y-3} = \frac{2970 + 165*y}{y}
2970*y = 2970 + 165*y*(y-3) \implies 2970*y = 2970*y - 2970*3+165*y^2 - 165*3*y
